  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟<strong>Star Soraight Fantasy: Magic to reach the sky</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/a7a59a9cf1f6adc3d975529befb03573.poster.avif?t=1748577194\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/a7a59a9cf1f6adc3d975529befb03573.webm?t=1748577194\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/a7a59a9cf1f6adc3d975529befb03573.mp4?t=1748577194\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tokino Sora-chan is suddenly whisked away to another world in the middle of her live performance! <br>A mysterious realm where her Hololive comrades and their precious items are scattered. <br>Can Sora-chan unravel the secrets of this strange world and make it back to her stage!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide Sora-chan’s story to a dazzling finale with your own hands!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/88e4032f2d5292f6b81f3e979f54c280.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/88e4032f2d5292f6b81f3e979f54c280.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟<strong>Explore and Conquer!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey between the vibrant “The Nun Nun Square” and the enigmatic “Mysterious Tower” in a blend of 2D and 3D.  <br>Tackle intricate terrains, battle formidable foes, and dive into dynamic action and exploration alongside Sora-chan!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/d3f9bc0d5dfa9d5173a80e413e628c07.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/d3f9bc0d5dfa9d5173a80e413e628c07.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟<strong>Team Up with the Holomen!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sora isn’t alone—her Holomen friends have also been transported to this strange world!  <br>Find them, harness their unique skills, and band together to conquer the tower’s depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/31c8f250116e59ae2c07e9afb892143b.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/31c8f250116e59ae2c07e9afb892143b.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟Power Up with Holomen Items!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scattered throughout the tower are special items imbued with the Holomen’s powers.  <br>Collect them to enhance Sora’s abilities and unlock new paths in your adventure.  <br>The more you find, the stronger you become!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/6e75cd6da18c50e605f2df524ddbe3a6.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/6e75cd6da18c50e605f2df524ddbe3a6.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟Ride the Sora Train and explore the tower with total freedom! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This incredible train whisks you instantly from the tower’s base to its deepest reaches, letting you move as you please. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for a 100% exploration rate as you uncover every corner of this tower!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/4d2d7010437439e1a7766e19a6e288de.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/4d2d7010437439e1a7766e19a6e288de.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong></strong><br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟Uncover the Secret of the Sora Coins!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt for elusive “Sora Coins” hidden within the tower.  <br>Gather as many as you can and deliver them to a mysterious character for exclusive rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/d7f6aaa020d7b29d570647a54e346cdf.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/d7f6aaa020d7b29d570647a54e346cdf.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟Sora’s Irresistible Charm!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond the thrilling main story, revel in Sora’s adorable dance moves, expressive poses, and vibrant emotions.  <br>Customize her look and soak in her charm at every turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras/1c7334718560c800f5832fa314e12dd4.avif?t=1748577194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3668950/extras_big/1c7334718560c800f5832fa314e12dd4.avif?t=1748577194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join Sora and the Holomen in Star Soraito Fantasy for a sparkling adventure filled with action, exploration, and heartwarming moments.</strong><br><strong>Solve the mysteries of another world and return to original world!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is published under CCMC Corp(※1)'s Indie game brand \"holo Indie\".(※2)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is allowed to be monetized under the examination and terms of \"holo Indie\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that any monetized derivative work games that include Cover Corp.'s content outside of holo Indie is not covered by these terms and is not allowed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※1. About CCMC Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CCMC Corp. is entrusted with website management (ex: steam) including, examination, publishing and other necessary tasks by Cover Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※2. About \"holo Indie\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >holo Indie's objective is to cooperate with hololive production fans and creators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a game brand that offers \"Game Creator Support Program\" for the derivative work games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For more details about \"holo Indie\", Please refer to the Cover Corp.'s \"Derivative work guidelines\".  <br>  </p>",
